  "notes": "Per spec Section 3.7: If provenance.type is 'merged', manifest MUST include merged_at and non-empty source_packs. Each source_pack MUST include stream, pack_digest, and artifacts. If attestations are recorded, they MUST be embedded_attestations array containing complete Sigstore bundles with mediaType, verificationMaterial, and dsseEnvelope."
}
